ALQ.MC.summary: Alquiber Quality, S.A. provides industrial and commercial vehicle rental services for SMEs and large companies in Spain. The company's fleet includes passenger cars, vans, SUVs, pick-ups, trucks, off-road, and adapted vehicles, as well as isotherms. It also sells used cars. The company was incorporated in 2000 and is based in Fuenlabrada, Spain. Alquiber Quality, S.A. is a subsidiary of Sebeca Ikap, S.L.
